sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Step
    participant R as Reader
    participant W as Writer
    participant DB as MySQL

    Note over S,DB: 최초 실행
    S->>R: open(ctx)
    R->>R: nextOffset = 0

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
    Note over S,DB: chunk 1, 2 정상 처리
    S->>W: write
    W->>DB: INSERT + commit
    R->>DB: nextOffset=100 저장
    end

    rect rgb(255, 224, 224)
    Note over S,W: chunk 3 처리 중 실패
    S->>W: write
    W--xS: 롤백 (update 호출 안됨)
    end

    Note over S,DB: 재시작

    S->>R: open(ctx)
    DB-->>R: nextOffset=100 복원

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
    Note over S,DB: chunk 3 재시도
    S->>W: write
    W->>DB: UPSERT (멱등)
    R->>DB: nextOffset=150 저장
    end
